594
00:50:33,500 --> 00:50:35,000
( Dampers Slamming)

595
00:50:37,500 --> 00:50:40,000
Hold it.

596
00:50:40,500 --> 00:50:42,000
Hold it!

597
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:44,000
Now ,  engage
the reversing engine!

