602
00:51:22,600 --> 00:51:25,100
( Softly):
Come on ,  come on ,  come on.

603
00:51:25,600 --> 00:51:27,100
Turn.

604
00:51:37,600 --> 00:51:39,100
Yes.

605
00:51:43,600 --> 00:51:46,100
It's going to hit!

606
00:51:57,600 --> 00:52:00,100
Jesus Christ.

607
00:52:13,500 --> 00:52:15,000
( Glass Tinkling)

608
00:52:19,500 --> 00:52:22,000
- ( Softly):Jesus.
- Hard to port!

609
00:52:22,500 --> 00:52:25,000
Crewman:
Hard to port!

